  "doc_id": "46120",
  "text": "Helical parameters were calculated using 3DNA (42). Sequence-independent measures were used based on vectors connecting the C1 0 atoms of the paired residues, to avoid computational artefacts arising from non-canonical base pairing. Program PBEQ-Solver (43) was used to calculate electrostatic potential map. All pictures were drawn using PyMOL v0.99rc6 [CITATION_1] . The coordinates of the crystallographic models have been deposited with the Protein Data Bank (PDB) with accession codes 3R1C, 3R1D and 3R1E.",
